sequenceDiagram
  title Sequence Flow: AI Deep Dive Log Query Process
  participant U as Support Staff
  participant UI as Web UI
  participant AI as AI Service
  participant API as Backend API
  participant DB as SQL Server

  U->>UI: Send AI prompt
  UI->>AI: Send prompt + context
  AI->>API: Tool call: Fetch logs
  API->>DB: Fetch log data
  DB-->>API: Return log data
  API-->>AI: Tool response: Log data
  AI-->>UI: Answer + summary
  UI-->>U: Stream response